item.title: Shippy.vn
item.description: Shippy is a group buying website where Vietnamese shoppers can group buy US’s products at a cheaper shipping cost. I was the co-founder and CTO of Shippy. Our techstack: Back-end: Ruby on Rails, SpreeCommerce, Sidekiq, PredictionIO Front-end: React, Redux Infra: AWS EC2, Cloudfront, S3 Shippy on angel.co Shippy on facebook Shippy’s website https://shippy.vn is now out of business. Shippy’s first version built with Ruby on Rails and Ember.
